2️⃣ Important Quick Facts
🔹 Earth

Shape → Geoid (Oblate spheroid)

Rotation → 24 hours

Revolution → 365 days

🔹 Important Rivers of India

Ganga → Longest river in India

Brahmaputra → Flows through Assam

Godavari → Longest river in South India

Narmada → Flows westward

🔹 Mountains

Himalayas → Young fold mountains

Highest peak → Mount Everest

🔹 Climate

Monsoon winds bring rainfall in India

Southwest monsoon → June to September

